FBIS4-41723 "drsov124_m_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-124 Daily Report 27 Jun 1994 Tajikistan Concept of Agricultural Development To Be Revised Concept of Agricultural Development To Be Revised LD2706150294 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Tajik 1200 GMT 27 Jun 94 LD2706150294 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network Tajik BFN [Text] A meeting took place in the Council of Ministers of the Republic, under the chairmanship of Abdulmadjid Samadov today. The issue relating to revising the concept of development of agriculture of the Republic was discussed in the meeting. The heads of the relevant ministries and departments and prominent scientists of the Tajik Academy of Sciences attended the meeting. It was pointed out in the meeting that the present concept of development of agriculture should be revised in the conditions of the present-day economic crisis of Tajikistan. The absence of foreign loans makes the farmers rely only on the use of home resources. [words indistinct] With the purpose of revising the concept of development of agriculture of the Republic, a working group has been established out of the scientists of the country's Academy of Sciences and prominent agricultural experts.
